{"tid":1132955,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony Xperia手機設計將不會追逐市場競爭 要能呈現Sony技術特色","createTime":"2019-04-30T16:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T12:34:28.000Z","uid":64694,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"22aadfd8cdec747330006b2f4dd79ea3a40cea30","tid":1132955,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T16:39:23.000Z","msg":"Sony Xperia手機設計上不會刻意迎合市場主流，而是以能夠呈現Sony技術特色並強調減法思維，不是功能越多越好，而是要適合才最好。<br />\n<br />\n除了今年在MWC 2019期間與Sony Mobile資深產品策劃經理染谷洋祐詢問Xperia 1所帶來改變，在此次Xperia 1於台灣揭曉亮相之際，Sony Mobile螢幕工程師佐野紘平、設計師石津雄登，以及技術市場推廣暨相機軟體工程師森田徹也針對Xperia 1螢幕、聲音、外觀與相機功能設計做分享，同時也強調在手機設計主要還是會以當時設定主軸為發想，並不會一昧追逐市場競爭對手所提出設計。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cool3c.com/article/143117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Farticle%2F143117&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1d3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=bb9dcc6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cool3c.com/article/143117</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">通常講出呢啲嘢係咪即係代表GG嘅開始？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"89698fa09d643c55b7529c822054405099155beb","tid":1132955,"uid":240918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T19:22:33.000Z","msg":"dxo mark 唔駛課金啦"},{"pid":"77c02888ed1bc802bc7d3ed48a6ba8f151346b3b","tid":1132955,"uid":34884,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T22:07:58.000Z","msg":"有道理<br />\n<br />\n因為sony點做都好<br />\n啲人都只係識買三星、華為同apple<br />\n<br />\n諗辦法養熟玩死忠好過啦"},{"pid":"4075a65c813b24561f4e6fbb843e616bac168bcd","tid":1132955,"uid":121697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T01:30:38.000Z","msg":"gg左啦<br />\n成個部門同其他合拼左<br />\n不過仲會繼續出新機咁解"},{"pid":"72caca126a3e53c51d743dc82c9209371ba80d1a","tid":1132955,"uid":173936,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T02:11:34.000Z","msg":"Sony特色：<br />\n- 主打Entertainment但冇3.5mm<br />\n- 有外置SD卡位、有雙卡，不過3揀2<br />\n- 中階係2年前規格同一年